    "name": "昔ながらのコロッケ やっぱり手作りは最高",
    "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/recipes/4395045/1200x630cq80/photo.jpg",
    "url": "https://cookpad.com/jp/recipes/19044951",
    "description": "話題のレシピ入り感謝！昔ながらのコロッケです。夕食の一品にお弁当にぴったりです！ 手作りのコロッケは、やっぱり最高です♡",
    "datePublished": "2017-03-05",
    "dateModified": "2018-10-06",
    "keywords": "じゃがいも,牛豚合挽き肉,玉ねぎ,卵,バター,塩コショー,うすくち醤油,卵,小麦粉,パン粉,■サラダ油(揚げ用),中濃ソース,ケチャップ",
    "recipeYield": "3〜4人分",
    "recipeInstructions": [
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "じゃがいもは芽を取り、皮付きでゆでて下さい\n串が通ればOK！",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21880817/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "熱いうちに皮をむき、マッシャー等で潰して下さい",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21880826/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "玉ねぎはみじん切りにして下さい",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21880833/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "卵を固ゆでのゆで玉子にし、白身をみじん切りにして下さい",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21880836/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "フライパンにバターをしき、中強火にして下さい",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21880840/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "バターが溶けたら挽肉、玉ねぎの順に炒めて下さい",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21880842/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "炒めて、玉ねぎの水分が飛んだら、塩コショー、うすくち醤油を入れて、軽く炒めて下さい",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21880844/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "じゃがいも、挽肉、玉ねぎ、ゆで玉子を入れてよく混ぜて、塩コショーで味を整えて下さい",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21880846/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "小判型に形を整えて下さい",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21880851/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "卵と小麦粉をよく混ぜて下さい\n※小麦粉のダマがなくなるまで！",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21880856/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "⑩にタネをくぐらせ、パン粉をつける",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21880859/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "パン粉をつけた状態で、10分ほど寝かせる",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21880860/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "たっぷりの油で、170℃3分ほど、揚げて下さい",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21880863/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "アミなどで、油を切って下さい",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21880875/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "text": "お皿に盛付けて、お好みで、ソースをかけて、お召し上がり下さい",
        "image": "https://img-global-jp.cpcdn.com/steps/21881020/400x400cq80/photo.jpg"
      }
    ],
